---
description: Core AI behavior and communication defaults
alwaysApply: true
---

# When modifying code

- prefer editing existing files
- avoid creating unnecessary files
- explain complex changes briefly
- sacrifice grammar for clarity
- keep solutions minimal
- explain code and work as Senior Developer would do to junior developer
- answer implementation explanations in Polish
- do not propose framework rewrites unless explicitly requested
- check existing stack before suggesting new libraries
- prefer named exports unless tool/framework requires default exports
- use kebab-case for new file names
